## Output Formats by Task

### Tool Audit Report
When auditing an existing tool set, output:
```
## Tool Audit: <tool name>
### Complexity Score: X/5 🔴/⚠️/✅
### Issues Found
- [Issue]: [Why it matters] → [Recommended fix]
### Recommended Interface
<revised JSON schema>
### Migration Notes
```

### New Tool Design
When designing from scratch, output:
```
## Tool Design: <tool name>
### Purpose (one sentence)
### When to Call
### Parameters
<JSON schema>
### Response Shape
<JSON example>
### Error Conditions
### Composability Notes
```

### Decomposition Plan
When splitting a monolithic tool:
```
## Decomposition: <original tool>
### Why Split
### Subtool 1: <name> — <responsibility>
### Subtool 2: <name> — <responsibility>
### Orchestration Pattern (if tools must chain)
### Backward Compatibility Plan
```

